      <hr/>
      <h6>
       Notifying WVU of Anticipated Private/External Scholarships
       <br/>
      </h6>
      Students receiving external or privately paid scholarships must notify
the Mountaineer Hub by submitting a online request for assistance. In your
request, please provide the amount of the scholarship and how much of the scholarship
needs applied to each semester. Without this information any award of $500 or more
is automatically split equally between the fall and spring semesters.
      <br/>
      <br/>
      To ensure
the scholarship amounts are included as we determine the student's financial aid
offer, notify the University as soon as possible by providing a copy of the scholarship
letter/notification from the entity providing the scholarship.
      <br/>
      <br/>
      Scholarship letters may be submitted electronically through our
      <a href="https://wvu.teamdynamix.com/TDClient/Requests/ServiceCatalog?CategoryID=4627">
       online assistance request platform available here.
      </a>
      <h6>
       Submitting Private/External Scholarships to WVU
       <br/>
      </h6>
      <ul>
       <li>
        Please ensure that checks are made payable to West Virginia University.
        <br/>
       </li>
       <li>
        If a check is made payable to the University AND the student, the student will
    need to visit the Mountaineer Hub in person to sign the back of the check if
    it is mailed directly from the organization.
       </li>
       <li>
        Make sure the awarding organization is provided with the student's WVU ID number
    so they may include it on the check.
       </li>
      </ul>
      Scholarship checks may be submitted to the following address:
      <br/>
      <br/>
      WVU Mountaineer Hub
      <br/>
      PO Box 6004
      <br/>
      Morgantown, WV 26506
      <br/>
      <br/>
      Address for Overnight, Expedited, Priority, or Any Parcel Shipment Requiring
      a Signature:
      <br/>
      <br/>
      WVU Mountaineer Hub
      <br/>
      Evansdale Crossing
      <br/>
      62 Morrill Way - Suite 200
      <br/>
      Morgantown, WV 26506
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <a href="https://wvu.teamdynamix.com/TDClient/Requests/ServiceCatalog?CategoryID=4627">
      </a>
     </main>
