      <div class="u-wvu-chunk pms-432-c background">
       <h3>
        Requirements for Priority Scholarship Consideration
       </h3>
       <ol>
        <li>
         Complete Undergraduate Admissions Application
         <br/>
        </li>
        <li>
         <span style="font-size: 1em;">
          High School Transcript
         </span>
        </li>
        <li>
         <span style="font-size: 1em;">
          ACT / SAT Scores
         </span>
        </li>
       </ol>
       <p>
        If funding is available, students applying after the priority deadline date may
    receive scholarship consideration. Some scholarships may have earlier dates,
    so please review all deadlines for the various scholarships carefully.
       </p>
